cSetAttribute.name: cSetAttribute
cSetAttribute.desc: This is the ID of the `Set Attribute` effect of the xsEffectAmount function

usage.explanation: This sets the attribute 0 (HP) of unit 74 (militia) to 100 (the value)

cModResource.name: cModResource
cModResource.desc: This is the ID of the `Modify Resource` effect for the xsEffectAmount function

usage.explanation: This adds 100 to the current food amount. Alternatively, `cAttributeSet` may be used to set the food amount to 100

cEnableObject.name: cEnableObject
cEnableObject.desc: This is the ID of the `Enable (or disable) Object` effect for the xsEffectAmount function

usage.explanation: This disables the unit 74 (militia). Alternatively, `cAttributeEnable` may be used to enable an object instead

cUpgradeUnit.name: cUpgradeUnit
cUpgradeUnit.desc: This is the ID of the `Upgrade Unit` effect for the xsEffectAmount function

usage.explanation: This replaces all units 74 (militia) with 75 (man at arms) on the map and also disables unit 74 and enables unit 75

cAddAttribute.name: cAddAttribute

cMulAttribute.name: cMulAttribute
